com.iver.cit.gvsig.fmap.layers.layerOperations
Interface VectorialData

All Known Implementing Classes:
FLayerFileVectorial, FLayerGenericVectorial, FLayers, FLayerVectorialDB, FLyrAnnotation, FLyrGT2, FLyrSecuential, FLyrVect, Topology, VoronoiAndTinInputLyr
public interface VectorialData

Interface that layers with vector data must implement.

Has methods for supporting the visitor pattern on the vector data features.
